{"tid":1588591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路祭習近平可得民心","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T01:51:11.000Z","uid":312147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a3736c61b290f5aa11cb137fcba0ca307a5080","tid":1588591,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"受此post啟發:<br />\n10月1日 全港路祭習近平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想加幾句自己嘅觀察<br />\n去肯定做呢樣野唔係玩膠<br />\n係真係可以對準政權同埋有效！<br />\n<br />\n我對大陸比較熟悉<br />\n我身邊好多響國企做野嘅朋友<br />\n（安全關係 我就唔自爆邊個省）<br />\n啲員工今年開始 要用一個叫「學習強國」嘅app學習偉大嘅習帝思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（相關資料可以睇<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/学习强国）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%89&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f58044ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/学习强国）</a><br />\n仲要做題目刷分數<br />\n每個月最低分個啲會俾人捉去照肺<br />\n於是出於恐懼嘅心態<br />\n大家就要嘥啲時間得閒就用下個「學習強國」<br />\n呢件事係搞到全部員工都屌晒老母（係大陸人！唔係香港個啲）<br />\n係，你冇聽錯，而家全部人都屌鳩緊習大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲大陸人雖然俾人洗腦洗到好撚愛國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係佢地愛國唔等於愛習大大</span><br />\n而家係習大大搞鳩緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果大家路祭習大大<br />\n佢地心裡面會好爽有人幫佢地出氣<br />\n<br />\n輸出革命要好似溫水煮蛙咁一步步黎<br />\n你一黎就反共，好多大陸人跟唔到<br />\n但由反習大大開始，會有好多人支持<br />\n甚至「非習派」都會煽風點火<br />\n<br />\n所以10月1大家識做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"598cb22140c2e4395979701c68659dc60fff5652","tid":1588591,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:37:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"fc4b8c906cef32e8fddac2dffbaa271214fe7c92","tid":1588591,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"習大暴政<br />\n天滅中共"},{"pid":"4de8786aed3b38d97b30c33733bd2fd5a50758a3","tid":1588591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"26e8f720a673e41e0fc50266dca1fae4601255cf","tid":1588591,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:41:17.000Z","msg":"#Chinazi 同反習一齊搞"},{"pid":"64823b035db1d516e2272c1ecbd84086fd1b424e","tid":1588591,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"佢地睇撚到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502228bce5ac3c70a2b26e67318b856e621ad7d8","tid":1588591,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"又做除惡滅罪法會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f339d6c802e5d56a71d0a9afaf55ef05d1e725","tid":1588591,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64823b035db1d516e2272c1ecbd84086fd1b424e","tid":1588591,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"佢地睇撚到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"呢排封VPN封得好勁<br />\n但過左10月頭就會有好多人睇到<br />\n總會輸出到大陸<br />\n做就岩"},{"pid":"ea61788056431b41c714ac6432da9cb5aaac8bb8","tid":1588591,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">㷫<br />\n<br />\n足<br />\n<br />\n七<br />\n<br />\n十<br />\n<br />\n年</span></span></span>"}]}